Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.86,0:48:06.98,Cartello BASE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fs30\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\fnArial\pos(166.301,50.8)}Anteprima
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.36,0:48:07.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Non dirmi che la macchina\N in cui è salita Ayumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.82,0:48:09.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...è quella del rapitore\N che uccide le bambine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.49,0:48:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aspettami, Ayumi!
